"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-product-recommendations-lifestyle-how-to-watch-2024-olympics-track-and-field-online-1235072824\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByJohn Lonsdale  If you purchase an independently reviewed product or service through a link on our website, Rolling Stone may receive an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\", \"score\": 0.994643047615474, \"rank\": 0.0053858038794255035, \"text\": \"Lonsdale\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lonsdale_Street\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.9999999991387085, \"rank\": 8.563462199228743e-10, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dash for gold is starting to heat up.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top athletes in the world have already made the2024 Paris Olympicsone to remember, from unforgettable moments fromgymnasticstoswimming.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The track and field competition is now underway in the City of Light, as Noah Lyles and Sha'Carri Richardson secured medals earlier this week.\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are still more highly anticipated events scheduled through the rest of the week - here's how to watch them all online.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the shot put to the 100-meter dash, the track and field events are in full swing, with Team USA athletes, including the fastest woman in the world and silver medalistSha'Carri Richardson, two-time gold medalist Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone, gold medalist Noah Lyles, gold medalist Sydney Moon, and more Olympians vying for spot at the top of the podium in this month's games.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9984903451687798, \"rank\": 0.0014092477842245613, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999731189749, \"rank\": 2.6880850424327315e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999942011418048, \"rank\": 5.755379270077688e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999942011418048, \"rank\": 5.755379270077688e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 0.9999999975666469, \"rank\": 2.3103258972287433e-09, \"text\": \"Moon\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how to watch the upcoming track and fieldParis Olympicsevents online at home without cable.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles, who won a gold medal in the 100m event, will compete in the men's 200m semifinals today, Aug. 7, at 2:10 p.m.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET / 11:10 a.m. PT.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.738961186859978e-18, \"text\": \"PT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read on for our full streaming guide to watch Paris Olympics track and field this week.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carrying local channels like NBC and national networks like USA,DirecTV Streammakes watching many of the Paris Olympics events easy.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9665598001091448, \"rank\": 0.0323432832859097, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999998457406155, \"rank\": 1.5418386643602547e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The live TV streamer offers a five-day free trial upfront to tune into upcoming track and field athletics, then costs $79.99 a month to keep your subscription.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DirecTV Stream is one of the most comprehensive live TV streaming services with up to 160+ channels, including local channels, regional sports networks, and all popular national channels.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DirecTV Stream\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DirecTV_Stream\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Packages start at $79.99 a month and all subscriptions start with a five-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are not sure which streaming service will air a specific track and field event, you can not go wrong tuning in with aPeacocksubscription.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streaming service broadcasts all Paris Olympic events, as well as replays and more.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999881461009, \"rank\": 1.1853716297925941e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can get a plan starting at $7.99 a month, making it one of the cheapest monthly options out there for streaming the Olympic games.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock includes 50+ channels in its base subscription, starting at $7.99 a month.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will stream all Summer Olympic events, plus event replays and more.Bonus: You can save an extra 17% over the year with a Peacock annual subscription, which costs $79.99.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trying to watch the Olympics in another country?\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We suggest springing for a virtual private network, orVPN.\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, you can watch upcoming track and field Olympic events with a VPN on channels that you would not normally get where you live.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's that simple.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ExpressVPN offers internet access in up to 160 locations around the world, making it easy to tune into local networks to watch live sports coverage online.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plans start at $12.95 a month (but right now you can get three months free when signing up for an annual package).\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus: All your info will be kept secure and private.\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fuboTVoffers local and national networks alike, including NBC, USA, and the E!\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3183, \"end\": 3186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9665598001091448, \"rank\": 0.0323432832859097, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999998457406155, \"rank\": 1.5418386643602547e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Network, all of which will air track and field events over the next few weeks.\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fubo is one of the few streamers that comes with a seven-day free trial.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, subscribers pay a $79.99 monthly subscription fee.\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"fuboTV offers up 275+ channels, with a ton of sports and local stations included in its plans.\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3422, \"end\": 3428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FuboTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"fuboTV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FuboTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FuboTV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Packages start at $79.99 per month, with a seven-day free trial to start.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TValso offers a variety of channels, including NBC, USA, and E!, in its ad-supported package.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3651, \"end\": 3654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9665598001091448, \"rank\": 0.0323432832859097, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3656, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999998457406155, \"rank\": 1.5418386643602547e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A plan will run you $76.99 a month, but you can tune into track and field events and more starting with a three-day free trial.\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TV bundles together all of Hulu's own content, along with over 95 live TV channels that make it a cinch to watch most games online.\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3868, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hulu\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hulu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscriptions also include ESPN+ and Disney+ at no additional cost.\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 4040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hulu + Live TV costs $76.99 a month after a three-day free trial.\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans can check the official2024 Olympics schedulefor a complete list of upcoming track and field events, including when to watch Richardson, Lyles, and more over the next few weeks.\", \"from